fields.name: 15 x ROX protein bar, 55 g
fields.description: Rox Protein Bar from Fast Nutrition is a protein-rich snack with fantastic taste and texture. This bar consists of three layers - with a soft texture in the middle, creamy middle layer and covered with a crispy casing. These bars are gluten and palm oil free.

fields.name: 15 x Goodlife Low Sugar, 50 g
fields.description: Each Goodlife protein bar provides approximately 190 kcal, 16 g of protein and 20 g of carbohydrates. Goodlife is perfect as a snack at any time of the day.

fields.name: Dalblads 15 x Swebar, 55 g
fields.description: Dalblads is a Swedish dietary supplement company that was founded in the late 90s. The company's focus is doping - free, tested and affordable products with high efficiency and good taste. Dalblads is aimed at all exercisers and elites who want to perform or feel better.

fields.name: Star Vegan Protein
fields.description: Vegan Protein Bar is a vegan and gluten-free protein bar from Star Nutrition. The bar combines a fabulous taste and texture with good nutritional values. Protein bar with a high protein and fiber content. It is a tasty bar that can be used as a good and filling snack or as a useful substitute for your regular sweets.

fields.name: Barebells Double bite Protein Bar
fields.description: Double bite Protein Bar contains plenty of protein, tastes wonderfully good and has a fantastic mouthfeel. It also contains no added sugar and with a high content of fiber, it is excellent as a luxury snack.

fields.name: Ultimate Diet Complex
fields.description: Ultimate Diet Complex from Star Nutrition is a good, low-calorie and filling powder developed to give you a complete nutritional profile during the diet. Ultimate Diet Complex can be used for weight loss or maintaining a healthy weight for both active and sedentary individuals.

fields.name: Mutant Whey 4,5 kg
fields.description: Mutant Whey consists of four different protein complexes that are absorbed in the different phases of the digestive process. This means that your body can utilize the essential and non-essential amino acids of whey protein to the max.

fields.name: Vegan Protein, 750 g
fields.description: Weidar Vegan protein contains a pea powder that is equivalent to whey protein. It is in turn enriched with rice protein which is beneficial for your muscle building. Feel free to try the vegan protein from Weidar, which has plenty of protein-rich ingredients from the plant kingdom. The product is added to your training drink to increase the taste and nutritional value.

fields.name: 100% Casein Gold Standard
fields.description: Optimum Nutritions 100 % Casein Gold Standard är ett kvalitativt proteintillskott som inte behöver tas direkt före eller efter träning för bästa resultat. Det har nämligen en ”tidsfördröjd” verkan och passar därför bra under hela dagen, men framför allt precis innan du går och lägger dig. Då får musklerna en jämn ström av aminosyror under hela natten och goda förutsättningar att återhämta sig.

fields.name: Super Meal, Supermass Nutrition
fields.description: Pro-Meal - An innovative meal replacement with a cruel taste and excellent nutritional values from Supermass Nutrition !. A tasty and simple alternative with excellent nutritional value when you have no time or desire to cook a whole meal. Developed especially for athletes: the product ensures that your body gets all the ingredients it needs for optimal recovery and development!.

fields.name: 24 x NOCCO BCAA, 330 ml
fields.description: NOCCO BCAA is the thirst quencher that has taken the fitness industry by storm! Quenching your thirst with something tasty and refreshing is nice enough as it is, but also being able to do it with content that is only beneficial for your active lifestyle makes it all extra good.

fields.name: 16 x Gainomax Recovery, 250 ml
fields.description: Gainomax Recovery - A potent milk-based recovery drink. Contains high quality protein in combination with carbohydrates and important nutrients. With its well-thought-out combination of fast protein, slow protein and fast carbohydrates, Gainomax Recovery provides all the nutrients needed for fast and efficient recovery.

fields.name: 12 x Reign Energy, 50 cl
fields.description: Reign Total Body Fuel is a new functional drink on the market that has just been launched. Reign Total Body Fuel contains everything a functional drink should; lots of caffeine for increased energy and concentration, Vitamin B3, B6 & B12 to keep your vitamin intake on top, l-arginine, and last but not least BCAA.

fields.name: 24 x Red Bull Energy SugarFree
fields.description: Red Bull's energy drinks are appreciated all over the world by top athletes and students, during demanding working days and during long car journeys. Caffeine has been used for its stimulating effect on the human body since time immemorial and is found naturally in over 60 plants. Among other things, caffeine has the ability to give an increased feeling of alertness and helps to stimulate the ability to concentrate. One can of Red Bull Energy Drink 250ml contains 80mg of caffeine.

fields.name: 24 x Monster Energy, 355 ml
fields.description: Monster Energy is a carbonated energy drink from Monster. The energy drink is the first in Monster Energy's taste series and is enriched with most vitamins, including taurine, ginseng, guarana and caffeine. This drink is suitable for you who need extra energy and love the taste of the original from Monster Energy! This jar is the slim variant!.

fields.name: The Curse, 250 g + T-shirt
fields.description: The Curse - The PWO from Cobra Labs that makes you obsessed with weights! Efficient and well-composed performance enhancer for the brave! This deal includes a T-shirt at a discounted price!.

fields.name: Baspaketet, HERS
fields.description: The basic package HERS contains three key products that all active people benefit from. The products in the package are also the products that are included in our diet plan for girls.

fields.name: 4 x EAA+ Amino, 400 g
fields.description: 4 x EAA + Amino, a dietary supplement from Delta Nutrition, is a highly-concentrated supplement with essential amino acids.

fields.name: Delta Growth Pack (Creatine)

fields.name: 24 x Star Nutrition Amino 330 ml
fields.description: Mix your own favorites at Star Nutrition Amino Energy! You can choose between 3 different flavors. Carbonated drinks with amino acids and caffeine are popular products - with every right. They taste good, liven up and are a convenient way to absorb amino acids during the day.
